# 🔁 DATA PIPELINE (CRON)

```text
Check Sync Heartbeat (meta)
   ↓
Fetch New Trades
   ↓
Resolve Winners (CLOB Token API)
   ↓
Bulk Upsert (trades table)
   ↓
Background Task: Incremental leaderboard_stats refresh
   ↓
Background Task: 14-day retention cleanup
```

